        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.sayed-athar-husain-rizvi-&-sayed-maqsood-athar": [
            "1. From the previous chain from al-Hassan from Sandal from Yazid b. Khalifa from Abi Abdillah (a.s.) who said: Whoever regularly recites Surah Najm during the day or night would become praiseworthy and conspicuous among the people, would be forgiven (his sins) and would become popular and amiable among the people."
          ]
